      <title>欧洲天然气和电力价格因创纪录的风暴而受到挤压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/european-gas-and-electricity-prices-tumble-as-wind-power-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲能源价格暴跌，天然气期货触及六个月低点，原因是新的大西洋风暴带来了不合时宜的温暖并促进了风力发电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/european-gas-and-electricity-prices-tumble-as-wind-power-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 08:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
